"{\"uid\": \"si.com-fannation-boxing-algerian-boxer-imane-khelif-shines-amidst-controversy-at-the-paris-olympics-01j4f771wvx8\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Mohamed Bahaa  In a compelling and emotional bout at the Paris Olympics, Algerian boxer Imane Khelif clinched a medal in the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 66-kilogram division.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 76, \"end\": 84, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9962129104393526, \"rank\": 0.003787288659526655, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 91, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her victory comes after a storm of controversy and online abuse centered around misconceptions about her gender, igniting broader debates about identity in sports.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 323, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif triumphed over Hungary's Anna Luca Hamori with a decisive 5:0 win in the quarterfinals, ensuring her a minimum of a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7922704253388779, \"rank\": 0.26064188613716155, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.9999999008200624, \"rank\": 9.841009105777987e-08, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This marked her second victory at the Paris Games, where she has faced immense pressure amidst her return to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy surrounding Khelif erupted due to claims from the International Boxing Association (IBA), banned from the Olympics since 2019, suggesting she failed an unspecified eligibility test due to elevated testosterone levels.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.165076930622928e-23, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 686, \"end\": 689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999983473844636, \"rank\": 1.6296948584141752e-06, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This issue has added fuel to the ongoing discussions about gender identity in sports, drawing attention from figures like former U.S. President Donald Trump and author J.K. Rowling, who perpetuated false narratives questioning Khelif\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s gender.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999999999522515, \"rank\": 4.337098846131842e-11, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 988, \"end\": 992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.265628641143709e-22, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During her first Olympic bout in Paris, Khelif's opponent, Angela Carini of Italy, withdrew from the match just 46 seconds in, citing emotional distress.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999946799107, \"rank\": 5.3202874789024024e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1126, \"end\": 1139, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.778107465628672, \"rank\": 0.19900502887375357, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This unusual development became a focal point for the debates over gender regulations in sports.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The victory against Hamori served as a moment of catharsis for the 25-year-old boxer from a small village in northwest Algeria.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999834714768484, \"rank\": 0.00016337539556867656, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After her victory was confirmed, Khelif knelt in the ring, overwhelmed by tears and joy, as she received applause from her supporters.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her emotional display continued as she embraced her coaches, basking in the support from her fans both in Paris and back home in Algeria.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1688, \"end\": 1693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999946799107, \"rank\": 5.3202874789024024e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1711, \"end\": 1718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999834714768484, \"rank\": 0.00016337539556867656, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI am happy for my daughter.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is courageous despite racist and sexist attacks to break her,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said her mother, Irene, on Algerian television.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1838, \"end\": 1843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_of_Athens\", \"score\": 0.9998959456918634, \"rank\": 0.00010379707221886825, \"text\": \"Irene\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_of_Athens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irene_of_Athens\"}, {\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9962129104393526, \"rank\": 0.003787288659526655, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the ring, Khelif showcased her skill with aggressive tactics, outmaneuvering Hamori with precision and resilience.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite facing resistance, Khelif maintained dominance throughout the fight, securing a unanimous decision from all five judges.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Khelif advances to the semifinals against Thailand's Janjaem Suwannapheng, her remarkable journey serves as a testament to her tenacity and dedication.\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2163, \"end\": 2171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"score\": 0.7676276114600545, \"rank\": 0.3027110459534101, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Paris Olympics marking a significant milestone in achieving gender parity in boxing, Khelif's triumph stands as a beacon of hope and progress in the sporting world.\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please wait while we load personalized content recommendations    \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026ABG-SI LLC-SPORTS ILLUSTRATED IS A REGISTERED TRADEMARK OF ABG-SI LLC.\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes o